            <h1>Rural and regional policy</h1>
            <div class="temaMobIngressImg" style="display: none;"></div>
            
            
            <div class="descriptionTextFull"><p>The government’s overall objectives for its rural and regional policy are as follows: </p>
<ul>
<li>that all people are free to choose their place of residence </li>
<li>to ensure equal living conditions and to utilise all resources throughout the country </li>
<li>to maintain settlement patterns in order to sustain and further develop the diversity of history, culture and the resources therein </li>
<li>to ensure that an active and target-oriented rural and regional policy helps generate added value, employment and welfare throughout the country</li></ul></div>
	    <div style="clear:both"></div>
	      
         </div>
         
         
                                
        
        
        
                            
